NUMBER 100
NAME Office, Guild Master
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
This study is small but well appointed. The walls are wood paneled and the
floor is a checkered black and white marble tiles. A massive black desk
and three large obsidian chairs dominates the room. The wall behind the desk
is completely taken up with a mural of a large keep resting amoung the peeks
of distant mountains. The only exit is the door you entered.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 65 ADJ1=267 ADJ2=312 VAL1=500 VAL2=91 VAL3=567 CLOSED LOCKED
EXTEND 0 with a large crimson key carved into it.
ITEM 1 420 ADJ1=87 ADJ2=355
EXTEND 1 paneling that seems to absorb all the sounds in the room
ITEM 2 201 ADJ1=189 ADJ2=25 ADJ3=216
ITEM 3 86 ADJ1=178 ADJ2=218
ITEM 4 1481
EXTEND 4 of a large keep hidden in the mountains
ITEM 5 540
IFLOGIN
  AFFECT 3645
  REMOVEITEM 8
  NEWITEM 8 550 VAL1=500 VAL2=567 VAL3=567 CLOSED LOCKED
  AFFECT 100
ENDIF
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
This massive desk is too large to have fit through the doorway. It is finely
crafted black oak and all of the fittings are of polished silver. The top is
polished black marble with crimson streaks under it's surface. A large scroll
is the only item on it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
This magnificent mural takes your breath away. The detail and craftsmenship
is so life like that you almost feel as if it is real. The massive keep rests
above a mist shrouded valley high within some towering snowcapped mountains.
You can barely see some flags fly from the upper tower, as you look closer
one of the flags seems to flutter as if in a breeze flashing a dark field with
a crimson dagger.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 5
Current Marks are...

Contracts up for consideration....

Past Marks...

Past declines...
*DESCRIPTION_END